12:28.464 --> 12:30.340
I see you've been
entertaining again.

12:31.468 --> 12:34.384
Got let off a little
steam now and again.

12:34.386 --> 12:36.555
Well, I'm sure you let
off plenty last night.

12:38.974 --> 12:40.307
You gotta be careful.

12:40.309 --> 12:42.352
You don't know what kind
of people are out there.

12:44.772 --> 12:46.480
