17:29.933 --> 17:32.849
He's the boss-man's nephew.

17:32.851 --> 17:34.352
[Miles] Hey, George.

17:34.354 --> 17:35.228
It was just a joke, buddy.

17:35.230 --> 17:36.269
Hey, George, come back here.

17:36.271 --> 17:37.272
Yo.

17:41.319 --> 17:42.402
