17:45.948 --> 17:47.615
Hey, Joan.

17:47.617 --> 17:49.032
How's it going?

17:49.034 --> 17:49.991
Can't complain.

17:49.993 --> 17:53.328
(boots slamming)

17:53.330 --> 17:55.123
[Donna] Never-ending
paperwork.

17:55.125 --> 17:58.334
It's not easy being a
woman in a man's world.

17:58.336 --> 18:00.171
