18:01.213 --> 18:02.381
Will you give us
some privacy, Donna?

18:03.465 --> 18:04.466
[Donna] Yes, sir.

18:11.014 --> 18:13.016
[Anson] And get
your feet off my desk.

18:17.312 --> 18:19.521
[Joan] And what can
I do for you today,

18:19.523 --> 18:22.316
oh great Mr. Anson, sir?

18:22.318 --> 18:23.942
