18:27.490 --> 18:29.156
So?

18:29.158 --> 18:31.075
Can't you just do
the usual casserole?

18:31.077 --> 18:33.368
The usual casserole?

18:33.370 --> 18:34.872
What's that supposed to mean?

18:36.707 --> 18:38.834
What am I gonna tell
this kid's family, huh?

18:41.003 --> 18:43.171
