you ever do that again.

18:51.263 --> 18:53.015
You hear me?

18:53.767 --> 18:57.059
Look, man, you got a problem?

18:57.061 --> 18:58.646
Talk to Frank.

19:01.107 --> 19:02.856
You watch yourself.

19:02.858 --> 19:04.985
Frank can only do so much.

19:09.823 --> 19:11.867
Now, got something
for you to do.

19:13.036 --> 19:15.661
Frank has asked you to
personally take care of this.

19:15.663 --> 19:18.247
