little bit of blood,

19:25.964 --> 19:28.385
and everyone gets the message.

19:32.430 --> 19:33.554
Anthony?

19:33.556 --> 19:36.682
Social worker at the
Downtown Youth Shelter.

19:36.684 --> 19:39.727
