step out of the shelter

19:39.729 --> 19:41.395
and onto the streets,

19:41.397 --> 19:43.732
trying to help these kids
clean their lives up.

19:45.068 --> 19:47.694
Well, it means a drop
in demand for us.

19:48.821 --> 19:50.570
You need to go and
send a message.

19:50.572 --> 19:53.907
(ominous atmospheric music)

19:53.909 --> 19:54.743
Are you deaf?

19:57.539 --> 19:58.373
No.

19:59.581 --> 20:01.332
No, I got this.

20:01.334 --> 20:04.126
