to shove me down, huh?

22:28.897 --> 22:30.357
I'm not a little girl anymore.

22:39.075 --> 22:40.285
Fuck.

22:40.909 --> 22:41.951
I can't do this.

22:41.953 --> 22:43.744
What's gotten into you?

22:43.746 --> 22:44.747
